<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM1.1">
<l>taiyoru tiṅkaḷun taraiviḷakkit taṇmaṇ ṭalamiṭṭu mācimuṉṉāḷ</l>
<l>aiyanuṇ maṇaṟkoṇṭu teruvaṇin taḻakiṉuk kalaṅkarit taṉaṅkatēvā</l>
<l>uyyavu māṅkolō veṉṟucol liyuṉṉaiyu mumpiyaiyun toḻutēṉ</l>
<l>veyyatōr taḻalumiḻ cakkarakkai vēṅkaṭa vaṟkeṉṉai vitikkiṟṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Cleaning the floor the whole month of tai, drawing a cool circle,</l>
<l>adorning the streets with beautiful, fine sand, decorating [them]</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of beauti[fication] during the first days of māci,</l>
<l>saying, ‘O bodiless god (Kāma)! Will it be possible [for me] to be saved?’</l>
<l>I have worshipped you and your brother.</l>
<l rend="indent">Will you be able to intend me for Him of Veṅkaṭam</l>
<l rend="indent">whose hand [holds] a unique discus that spits hot fire?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
